斯同場[影] |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002070008.aspx |accessdate=2020-02-07 |agency=中央通訊社 |date=2020-02-07 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128202344/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202002070008.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

